    "en": {
      "name": "Performage Cup Tricker",
      "effect": "If this card is in your hand: You can target 1 Xyz Monster on the field; detach 1 material from it, and if you do, Special Summon this card, then 1 Xyz Monster on the field loses 600 ATK. If this card is detached from an Xyz Monster and sent to the GY to activate that monster's effect: You can target 2 Xyz Monsters you control; detach 1 material from 1 of them, and if you do, attach it to the other as material. You can only use each monster effect of \"Performage Cup Tricker\" once per turn.",
      "pendulumEffect": "You can target 1 \"Performage\" Xyz Monster you control; attach this card to it as material. If a card(s) is added to your Extra Deck (except during the Damage Step): You can add 1 face-up \"Performage\" Pendulum Monster from your Extra Deck to your hand. You can only use each Pendulum Effect of \"Performage Cup Tricker\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
